New panel.<br>
Earth sits up in bed. Clock beside bed reads midnight or soon after.<br>
New panel<br>
Earth pulling on clothes.<br>
Earth: Man, that was wierd. I'm going for a walk. Should clear my head...<br>
New panel.<br>
Earth walking down a street. Dirty.<br>
Next coupla panels<br>
A hand grabs him, pulls him into an alley. The alley is quite narrow. There are three people standing in it, and Earth as well. One is holding Earth by his throat against a wall. His feet are several inches off the ground.<br>
Next panel.<br>
One of the thugs grins, revealing long, pointed incisors.<br>
Vampire: Well, I think our dial-a-meal has arrived at last.<br>
Next panel<br>
Vampire gets a surprised look on his face. There is a point of wood protruding through his throat, another through his heart.<br>
Next panel<br>
Vampire bursts into dust. An axe swings through the air, decapitating the other two vampires. Earth collapses on the floor.<br>
Next panel.<br>
Air is standing before Earth, a crossbow in either hand. Behind her is a man with reddish-orange hair. He's carrying an axe.<br>
Air: And now we are four.<br>
Next panel<br>
Air shows the tattoo on her hand. <p>'It's better to light a candle than curse the darkness, and better than both to remain unseen.'- NeoAngel. .................

